Class ApplicationController

java.lang.Object
control.ApplicationController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicationEligibilityController, ApplicationManagementController, ApplicationQueryController
public class ApplicationController extends Object implements ApplicationEligibilityController, ApplicationManagementController, ApplicationQueryController
The ApplicationController class manages all application-related operations in the BTO Management System. It handles application creation, eligibility checks, status updates (approval, rejection, withdrawal), and booking confirmation. Interfaces implemented: - ApplicationEligibilityController - ApplicationManagementController - ApplicationQueryController
